 management exceeding  billion will operate as avalon advisors llc   since its inception in  avalon has served san antonio clients from its houston headquarters and in  the firm opened a local office to expand its central and south texas presence significantly under the leadership of san antonio native rob mcclane   a san antoniobased and independently owned investment management firm matterhorn was founded in  to manage equity and fixed income portfolios for high net worth individuals family offices regional advisory groups and institutional investors throughout south texas   “we have long admired matterhorn’s stewardship approach and investment performance for the families they serve  they bring an invaluable group of people a strong culture consistent performance and a pursuit of excellence that aligns naturally with avalon and the families we will now serve together” said henry j lartigue avalon’s ceo and cio “such a significant partnership builds on our long standing relationships with leading san antonio and south texas families and enhances both our portfolio management and wealth advisory capabilities  both firms have earned a sterling reputation for transparency innovation wealth preservation and fiduciary responsibility and we will remain steadfastly committed to carrying these values forward   “we look forward to joining the avalon team and having our clients benefit from the expansion of overall resources and capabilities” said juan landa matterhorn’s ceo “the fact that we are committed to maintaining the continuity of our advisory teams means the investment management philosophy our clients have come to know and trust will not only be preserved but enriched”   avalon advisors’ san antonio office in mccombs plaza convenient to many of the firm’s existing clients is expanding to accommodate the additions to the avalon team   about avalon advisors llc   avalon is a houstonbased independent registered investment adviser offering investment management and financial advice for individuals families and institutions founded in  avalon offers a full suite of internally managed strategies including domestic and international equities and fixed income as well as access to select alternative strategies   download pdf back to resources avalon perspectives tpp is dead what now january   the possibilities of trumps us december   reversal rates are the next big challenge for central banks november   the good ole days arent coming back october   the federal reserves antivolcker inflation revolt august   why the fed needs to raise its inflation target august   is the rest of the world ditching america to trade with china august   has the federal reserve become congresss golden goose july   the fed must avoid the credibility trap june   why the fed needs to make a policy error may   the fed faces its antivolcker moment may   the feds critical global mandate april   why the federal reserve is all talk april   is the global middle class really here to stay april   quarterly and monthly notes monthly notemay  monthly noteapril  quarterly notefirst quarter  monthly notefebruary  monthly notejanuary  quarterly notefourth quarter  monthly notedecember  monthly notenovember  quarterly notethird quarter  monthly noteaugust  monthly notejuly  quarterly notesecond quarter  monthly notemay  news  press avalon advisors announces san antonio expansion december   avalon advisors announcement december   sam rines april   avalon advisors announcement october   viewpoints china march   commentary fourth quarter  second quarter  first quarter  fourth quarter  third quarter  second quarter   allen parkway suite  houston tx     e mulberry avenue suite  san antonio tx     avalon advisors llc  all rights reserved form adv  privacy policy  site map bing places for business bing places for business sign in using your microsoft account work account google account facebook account dont have an account create one